text: "Strutter" is a 1974 song by American rock band Kiss and is the third single from their debut studio album Kiss. It failed to chart. It has been covered by Extreme and The Donnas. It has appeared on numerous albums after its release. ==References== Category:1974 songs Category:Kiss (band) songs Category:The Donnas songs Category:Glam rock songs Category:Hard rock songs
